uivalent financing.", "bbox": [204.2, 1121.5, 948.2, 1142.3]}, {"text": "Convertible Debt and Senior Subordinated Note Debt", "bbox": [183.3, 1178.7, 631.7, 1199.5]}, {"text": "The Company determines fair value of its convertible debentures based upon the debentures’ quoted market", "bbox": [204.2, 1214.6, 1104.7, 1235.4]}, {"text": "value.", "bbox": [162.5, 1239.6, 212.8, 1260.4]}, {"text": "Interest Rate Risk", "bbox": [183.3, 1296.8, 331.7, 1317.6]}, {"text": "The Company has total debt outstanding at December 31, 2007 of $856.0 million, of which $349.9 million", "bbox": [204.2, 1332.7, 1094.0, 1353.5]}, {"text": "or 41% carries a fixed rate of interest. The remaining debt balance is primarily comprised of $391.1 million in", "bbox": [162.5, 1357.7, 1082.2, 1378.5]}, {"text": "term loans under the Credit Agreement and $115.0 million outstanding under a receivables purchase agreement.", "bbox": [162.5, 1382.7, 1097.8, 1403.5]}, {"text": "The weighted average interest rate on these borrowings at December 31, 2007, excluding deferred financing costs", "bbox": [162.5, 1407.7, 1112.2, 1428.5]}, {"text": "and commitment fees, was approximately 5.8%.", "bbox": [162.5, 1432.7, 564.8, 1453.5]}, {"text": "55", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}